# Docs-First Library Work

`docs/` is the implementation source of truth while `forms-core` is being
developed. Before changing public API, architecture, validation behavior,
server-error lifecycle, array behavior, patch behavior, release workflow, or
review rules, update the matching canonical doc first.

If code and docs disagree, treat the PR as blocked until the same change either
updates the docs or brings the code back to the documented contract.
